---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 504
  - Title: Christ in Islâm
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Trust in God
---
Jesus (Peace be upon him!) said, ‘Do not worry about to-morrow's food,
for if to-morrow is one of your periods your provisions will come in
it along with your periods; and if it is not one of your periods, do
not worry about other people’s periods.’
